    • compareTo

      public int compareTo(Airplane other)
      Compares this airplane to another airplane based on their maximum speed and range. Airplanes are first compared by maximum speed in ascending order. If their maximum speeds are equal, they are compared by range in descending order.
      Specified by:
      compareTo in interface Comparable<Airplane>
      Parameters:
      other - The other airplane to compare with.
      Returns:
      A negative integer, zero, or a positive integer as this airplane is less than, equal to, or greater than the specified airplane.
